description:
In this episode we head deeper into Tango's Decked Out 2 mini-game. Each week of the game is called a Phase. The Hermits compete to get the most Victory Tomes each Phase so that they are awarded the most points. Here is how my Phase 1 runs went.

Decked Out 2 Tutorial: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aoVVCwx6k1w&t
